Add atom.cpp, atom.h, fix_bd_AOUP.cpp, fix_bd_AOUP.h, atom_vec_active.cpp and atom_vec_active.h to the lammps src folder.
Compile lammps as a library (for example: "make mpi mode=lib" in src folder)
Copy Lammps_drivensystem_run.cpp, AOUP_input.in and Makefile to a folder where you want to run the simulations.
Replace the path to lampps in the Makefile file
Type "make" to compile Lammps_drivensystem_run.cpp. 
Run simulation as "./Lammps_drivensystem_run.out 1 AOUP_input.in tau Pe gamma"

